data.description: 3BR/2BA home w/1 car garage nestled on 2+ acres with access to Wakulla County's hidden gem...Lake Ellen. Living room has wood burning fireplace and kitchen countertops upgraded to Quartz. In addition to LR have a separate nicely sized family room. Split floorpan. House is not in flood zone. Yard features sooo much privacy and room to move!!
